Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tubig Dayang Primary School in the Municipality of South Ubian, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Abdulcadil Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 664
An Act Changing the Name of the Tubig Dayang Primary School in the Municipality of South Ubian, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Hadji Abdulcadil Primary School
Section 1. The name of the Tubig Dayang Primary School in the Municipality of South Ubian, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Hadji Abdulcadil Primary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
